<a name="bone_bladed_claymore"></a>
<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Bone Bladed Claymore</strong>
<font size=-1>(<a href="/prices/item/bone_bladed_claymore.shtml">View Going Price</a>)</font><BR>
Skill: <a href="/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">2H Slash</a><BR>
Damage per second - 7.78<BR>
Damage 17 - Delay 45<BR>
Weight: 9.9 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/paladin/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">PAL</a>, <a href="/ranger/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">RNG</a>, <a href="/shadow_knight/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">SHD</a>, <a href="/warrior/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">WAR</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (Lore) <BR>
(AGI -8) </font>
<BR>
Dropped in Befallen by the Troll Shadowknight.<BR>
<BR>
Avg. Price Overall: 72pp (62 quotes)<BR>
Last 30 Days: 39pp (6 quotes)<BR>

