<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This weapon is really bad because of the -8agi so if you want to buy one you should not...if i was the buyer i would rather look for a BIBS...but if you dont have enough money for BIBS...buy BBC but you will have a hard time selling it.</font></td></tr></table>
