<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I use this weapon and it is great. I can hit for a constant DMG of 30 points and a critical hit of as high as 62. Sure it does -8 to AGI but a couple of rings or good magic armor and you are ready to kick major butt!<BR>
<BR>
Willwalace of the Karana server</font></td></tr></table>
