<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Sanral Brightember</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-03-20 06:07:29</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>A really great weapon for ranger's imho. The -8agi is no great loss to most rangers past 15th level.<BR>
<BR>
After level 21 when you max out your double attack skill, it will outdamage a pair of 6/22 weapons such as the SSoM and a silvery war axe.</font></td></tr></table>
<BR>
<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Pureheart</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-03-26 15:16:06</font></td></tr><tr>
