<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Sirk</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-04-01 19:04:46</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Don't bother getting this weapon. Why? Because before lvl 20 the most you can hit for non crit is 29. The Dwarven 2h axe hits that much anyways. It might not be magic but it costs far less (like 15plat) and dosen't have the agilility neg modifier. After 20 you should probably be able to afford a BIBS anyways, which we all know is far better than either.</font></td></tr></table>
